title: Recap: Tech drops 5-4 battle to #17 Texas - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Recap: Tech drops 5-4 battle to #17 Texas - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – Texas Tech (22-24, 5-11) dropped a back-and-forth battle with No. 17 Texas (33-15-1, 8-5), 5-4, Friday night in Lubbock.
